    <h2>Contour Level Selection</h2>
    <p>You have now learned the basic principles of the <a href="http://earthserver.eu" target="_new">EarthServer</a> CryoService such as selecting the product of your choice, a time of interes, choosing between point or rivershed statistics as well as limiting the statistics to certain contour levels.</p>
    <p>Feel free to close this tutorial and enjoy discovering spatio-temporal properties of snow coverage!.</p>
</section>

